        _ = (c / p) * eLorentzNorm (algebraMap ℝ 𝕂 ∘ NNReal.toReal ∘ g₁) p 1 μ + (c / p) * eLorentzNorm (algebraMap ℝ 𝕂 ∘ NNReal.toReal ∘ g₂) p 1 μ + (c / p) * eLorentzNorm (algebraMap ℝ 𝕂 ∘ NNReal.toReal ∘ g₃) p 1 μ + (c / p) * eLorentzNorm (algebraMap ℝ 𝕂 ∘ NNReal.toReal ∘ g₄) p 1 μ := by
